   "source": [
    "# Customer Segmentation Analysis\n",
    "\n",
    "## Objective\n",
    "Segment customers based on their purchasing behavior.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Amaç\n",
    "Müşterileri harcama ve sipariş davranışlarına göre segmentlere ayırmak."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "a814cd05-305c-4da6-9e80-7095657e880a",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "\n",
    "np.random.seed(42)\n",
    "\n",
    "n = 200\n",
    "\n",
    "df = pd.DataFrame({\n",
    "    \"customer_id\": range(1, n+1),\n",
    "    \"orders\": np.random.randint(1, 20, n),\n",
    "    \"total_spent\": np.random.randint(50, 1000, n)\n",
    "})\n",
    "\n",
    "df.head()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "122cfa2a-e6d5-432e-b589-d64b7f4a03f1",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def segment_customer(row):\n",
    "    if row[\"total_spent\"] > 700:\n",
    "        return \"High Value\"\n",
    "    elif row[\"total_spent\"] > 300:\n",
    "        return \"Mid Value\"\n",
    "    else:\n",
    "        return \"Low Value\"\n",
    "\n",
    "df[\"segment\"] = df.apply(segment_customer, axis=1)\n",
    "\n",
    "df.head()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "6fb6ccf8-106e-4f96-b2d0-49d50225840a",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "df[\"segment\"].value_counts()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "e1e274f7-4e15-49fa-ae70-e5bd0029b71a",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "df.groupby(\"segment\").agg({\n",
    "    \"total_spent\": \"mean\",\n",
    "    \"orders\": \"mean\"\n",
    "})"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "51739605-75a1-4d30-ae59-2aeb8e5ca3a6",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "\n",
    "df[\"segment\"].value_counts().plot(kind=\"bar\", title=\"Customer Segments\")\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "42db7870-8273-401c-8929-1c04c1f2969a",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "- High Value müşteriler korunmalı\n",
    "- Mid segment upsell ile büyütülmeli\n",
    "- Low segment için maliyet optimize edilmeli"
   ]
  },
